Class DateConverter

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.internet2.middleware.grouperClientExt.com.thoughtworks.xstream.converters.basic.AbstractSingleValueConverter

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ConverterMatcher, SingleValueConverter

    public class DateConverter
extends AbstractSingleValueConverter
    Converts a java.util.Date to a String as a date format, retaining precision down to milliseconds.
